                        <head>324. Memorandum of a Conversation, Department of State, Washington,
                            October 25, 1957, 10:30 a.m.<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d324fn1">Source: Department of State, Conference Files: Lot 62 D 181, CF
                                926. Secret. Drafted by <persName corresp="#p_DJ1">Dorman</persName>, approved by <persName>Dulles</persName> and
                                    <persName corresp="#p_GJNJ1">Greene</persName>, and circulated
                                to appropriate U.S. officials on October 25.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">MTW <gloss target="#t_MC1">MC</gloss>–8</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><hi rend="italic"><placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" type="conversation-or-meeting-date" when="1957-10-25T10:30:00-04:00">October 25, 1957, 10:30
                                        a.m.</date></hi></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <list type="subject">
                            <head>SUBJECT</head>
                            <item>VOA Transmitter on Cyprus</item>
                        </list>
