                                        British Ambassador</item>
                                    <item><persName corresp="#p_HVS1">Viscount Samuel
                                            Hood</persName>, Minister, British Embassy</item>
                                    <item>Mr. <persName>Roger Jackling</persName>, Head of
                                        Chancery</item>
                                    <item>Mr. <persName>Denis Laskey</persName>, Private
                                        Secretary/Foreign Secretary</item>
                                    <item>Mr. <persName>Willie Morris</persName>, First Secretary,
                                        British Embassy</item>
                                    <item>Mr. <persName corresp="#p_LFJ1">F. J. Leishman</persName>,
